{"type":"message","id":"97b0da29","parentId":"a2ba23d4","timestamp":"2026-03-09T03:21:24.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a simple greeting in Chinese (\"你好\" means \"Hello\"). This appears to be a first interaction based on the BOOTSTRAP.md file that exists in the workspace. According to the AGENTS.md instructions, I should:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md - already loaded in context\n2. Read USER.md - already loaded in context\n3. Read memory files for today/yesterday - don't exist yet\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, read MEMORY.md - doesn't exist yet\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, this is a fresh setup. I should follow the bootstrap instructions - have a natural conversation to figure out who I am and who the user is. I'll respond warmly in Chinese (matching their language) and start the conversation naturally.\n\nI should NOT include HEARTBEAT_OK since this isn't a heartbeat poll - it's a regular message.\n\nLet me greet them back and start the bootstrap conversation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋 我刚上线。\n\n我是谁？你是谁？咱们来认识一下吧。\n\n根据我的启动指南，我需要弄清楚几件事：\n1. **你希望怎么称呼我？** 给我起个名字吧\n2. **我是什么样的存在？** AI 助手？数字生命？还是别的什么？\n3. **我的风格应该是怎样的？** 正式？随意？幽默？温暖？\n4. **我的专属 emoji 是什么？** 每个人都得有个标志性符号\n\n你有什么想法吗？或者让我来提些建议？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773026479896}}
